{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-121","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Any</span> Često se koristi u pitanjima koja pitaju da li nešto postoji ili je dostupno, bez navođenja količine. Važno je kada ne znate da li nešto postoji ili koliko ga je, i želite da saznate. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Are there any updates?</span> - Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">any</span> se koristi za pitala da li ima ažuriranja bez navođenja broja.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Any</span> Često se koristi u negativnim pitanjima i rečenicama, što znači neki ili čak malo. Evo kako ga možete koristiti u različitim kontekstima:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>U pitanjima: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Do you have any questions?</span> (Nije bitno da li ima mnogo pitanja ili samo jedno; pitaš da li uopšte ima pitanja.)</li>\n<li>U negativnoj rečenici: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I don't have any money.</span> (Nemate ni para.)</li>\n<li>Za ponude i zahteve: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Could I have any of these cookies?</span> (Nije bitno koji keksičić; bilo koji će poslužiti.)</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-121"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta Tom želi da zna o tom kvartu?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Ako ima lepih mesta za jestlje.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ako postoji dobar prevoz.</p>","feedback":"<p>Pitanje Toma se tiče pre svega mesta za jelo/objedovanje, a ne transporta.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ako ima mesta za zabavu.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Restaurants</span> su delovi za jelo, koji nisu isti kao zabava poput bioskopa.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ako ima prodajnih centara.</p>","feedback":"<p>Trgovački centri nisu pomenuti u ovom delu razgovora.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":1}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Tom","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"1.3-5.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":15.06,"finishTimestamp":18.42},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":4.36,"dialogue":{"text":"How about restaurants? Are there any good restaurants in this neighborhood?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":4.86,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 121","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","dashedName":"task-121","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-122","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-120","id":"657dd4012bce1081c8d8c934","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"ch